{"view":"article","slug":"4x4-redux","category":"4x4","subcategory":null,"topDir":"4x4","title":{"en":"4x4 Redux Method","zh":"四阶魔方降阶法"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>4x4 Redux Method</strong></p><p><strong>Notation</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>R </strong>Outer layer</p></td><td><p><strong>r </strong>2 layers</p></td><td><p><strong>2R </strong>Inner Slice</p></td><td><p><strong>3r </strong>3 layers</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>F2C (Two Opposite Center)</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>1st Center</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u' r u r'\">u' r u r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u r u' r'\">u r u' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r F' r'\">r F' r'</span></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r' f r\">r' f r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"f r u r'\">f r u r'</span></p></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>2nd Center</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2' r2' F r\">r U2' r2' F r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r' F2 r2 U' r'\">r' F2 r2 U' r'</span></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2' r'\">r U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"z u' R2 u / r' F2 r\">z u' R2 u / r' F2 r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r2' F r\">r U' r2' F r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r2' F' r\">r U' r2' F' r</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(r U' r' U) r' F r\">(r U' r' U) r' F r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r2' F' r\">r U' r2' F' r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r2' F r\">r U' r2' F r</span></p></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>L4C (Last Four Centers)</strong></p><p>Do z move to make L4C on M slice. Solve centers into correct relative positions. Solve F center (3rd center), do x', solve current F center (4th center), do x', solve current F center (5th center), then 6th center will be solved automatically. One can also solve U center, then do x. Below is general idea on F center. </p><p><strong>Relative Positions</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Correct</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Wrong</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Wrong</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>F Center</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2' r'\">r U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U r'\">r U r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Edges</strong></p><p>Unsolved edge.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><a id=\"_Hlk6050220\"></a><strong>F10E (First Ten Edges)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>L2E (Last Two Edges)</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u' (R U' R') u\">u' (R U' R') u</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r' (U' R U) r\">r' (U' R U) r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u' (R U R' F R' F' R) u\">u' (R U R' F R' F' R) u</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r' (U' R' U R' F R F') r\">r' (U' R' U R' F R F') r</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>3x3</strong></p><p>Solve the cube as if it were a 3x3.</p><p><strong>Redux</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image66.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image68.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image70.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image72.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image74.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image76.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Parity Cases which </strong><a id=\"_Hlk5990715\"></a><strong>are Impossible on 3x3</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>OLL parity</strong></p><p>Odd flipped edges</p></td><td><p><strong>PLL parity</strong></p><p> Odd edge pair/corner swaps</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image78.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/en/image80.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r'\">r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r2 R2' U2 2R2 u2 2R2 u2 [U2]\">r2 R2' U2 2R2 u2 2R2 u2 [U2]</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>","zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">四阶魔方降阶法</strong></p><p><strong>转动记号</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p>外层</p><p><strong>R </strong></p></td><td><p>双层</p><p><strong>r</strong>或<strong>Rw</strong></p></td><td><p>内层</p><p><strong>2R </strong></p></td><td><p>三层</p><p><strong>3r</strong>或<strong>3Rw</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>F2C (前二心)</strong></p><p>做好两个相对的中心.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>第一心：</strong>找到一条棒放到底面左侧, 这里以白棒为例</p></td><td><p>组好另一条白棒放到底面右侧</p></td><td><p><strong>第二心：</strong>组好另一条黄棒放到顶面左侧</p></td><td><p>组好另一条黄棒放到顶面右侧</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>第二心</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(U') r U' r'\">(U') r U' r'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U r U2' r'\">U r U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(U') r U' r'\">(U') r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2' r'\">r U2' r'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>L4C (后四心)</strong></p><p>每次还原U心.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>还原第三心：</strong>z转体让白心朝左</p></td><td><p>x转体将棒放到顶面（如果有）, 转U层让棒靠左, 这里以红棒为例</p></td><td><p>在不破坏F2C的前提下, 组好另一个红棒靠右, 转r还原红面</p></td><td><p>x让红面到后</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong> <img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>第四心：</strong>还原顶心（绿）, 组好一条绿棒, 用藏移回的方法将它放到顶面左侧</p></td><td><p>再组好另一条绿棒, 用藏移回的方法将它放到顶面右侧</p></td><td><p>x让绿面到后</p></td><td><p><strong>第五心：</strong>还原顶心（橙）, 方法同第四心.还原完第五心后, 第六心自动还原</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>注：保证所有心的相对位置是正确的. </p><p><strong>相对位置</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong> <img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>正确</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>错误</strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r2 U2 D2 r2'\">r2 U2 D2 r2'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>错误</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>棱</strong></p><p>转外层将颜色匹配的一组棱都放到第二层 (或第三层). flip是翻棱公式<strong>R' F R F' R U' R'</strong>, 能原地翻转FR位置的棱.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p>都在前层</p></td><td><p>一个左层一个右层</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>u' flip u</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u2 flip u2</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>还原所有12组棱后, 四阶魔方降阶为三阶魔方.</p><p><strong>三阶</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image66.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image68.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><a id=\"_Hlk5990098\"></a><strong>三阶上不可能的特殊情况</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>O特 </strong>奇翻棱</p></td><td><p><strong>P特 </strong>奇置换</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image70.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image72.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(r U2' r' U2) r U2'(↓r U2 l' U2) (r U2' r' U2)↑ x' U2' r2\">(r U2' r' U2) r U2'(↓r U2 l' U2) (r U2' r' U2)↑ x' U2' r2</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u2 2R2 u2 2R2 U2 2R2\">u2 2R2 u2 2R2 U2 2R2</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>也可以还原完F心 (第三心), 做x', 还原当前F心 (第四心) , 做x', 还原当前F心 (第五心), 第六心就会自动还原.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image74.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image76.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image78.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/4x4-redux/zh/image80.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2' r'\">r U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U r'\">r U r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>已还原</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>未还原棱. 掌握一种拼法即可.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>F10E (前十棱)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>L2E (后二棱)</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>竖棱拼法</p></td><td><p>横棱拼法</p></td><td><p>竖棱拼法</p></td><td><p>横棱拼法</p></td></tr><tr